    "about": {
      "type": "section-accordion",
      "blocks": {
        "about-0": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Cotton",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-small",
            "text": "<p>Our clothing is made with the finest, responsibly sourced cotton, offering exceptional comfort while aligning with our commitment to sustainability.</p><p>To care for cotton clothing, machine wash in cold or warm water with a mild detergent, and avoid overloading the machine to prevent excess wear. After washing, tumble dry on a low or medium heat setting or line dry to maintain the fabric's quality and avoid excessive shrinkage.</p>",
            "aspect_ratio": 0.6
          }
        },
        "about-1": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Nylon",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-small",
            "text": "<p>Our nylon is carefully chosen for its durability and versatility, ensuring that our clothing is built to last. We are equally committed to responsible sourcing, contributing to a more sustainable future. </p><p>When caring for nylon clothing, machine wash in cold water using a gentle cycle to prevent damage to the fabric. Avoid using bleach and opt for air drying or tumble drying on a low heat setting to maintain the garment's shape and prevent overheating or melting.</p>",
            "aspect_ratio": 0.6
          }
        },
        "about-2": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Denim",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-small",
            "text": "<p>Sustainable denim involves using eco-friendly materials like organic cotton or recycled denim, employing efficient dyeing processes, reducing water and energy consumption, and ensuring ethical labor practices.</p><p>To care for denim clothing, turn it inside out and wash in cold water to preserve the color. Hang or line dry to prevent excessive shrinkage, and only iron if necessary, using medium heat to avoid damaging the fabric's structure.</p>",
            "aspect_ratio": 0.6
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "about-0",
        "about-1",
        "about-2"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "default_open": false,
        "title": "Fabric + Care",
        "heading_font_size": "heading-medium",
        "show_icon": false,
        "icon_name": "icon-award",
        "icon_size": 20,
        "width": "wrapper",
        "color_scheme": "",
