    "shipping": {
      "type": "section-accordion",
      "blocks": {
        "shipping-0": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon_name": "icon-fast-shipment",
            "icon_size": 20,
            "icon_color": "#32393e",
            "title": "Fast shipping",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-small",
            "icon_alignment": "left",
            "text": "<p>Our shipping policy is designed with your convenience in mind. We strive to provide efficient and reliable delivery services, with various shipping options to suit your preferences. You can count on us to keep you informed every step of the way, ensuring a seamless and worry-free shopping experience.</p>",
            "text_alignment": "text-left"
          }
        },
        "shipping-1": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon_name": "icon-box",
            "icon_size": 20,
            "icon_color": "#32393e",
            "title": "Order tracking",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-small",
            "icon_alignment": "left",
            "text": "<p>Stay in control of your order with our easy-to-use tracking feature. As soon as your order is on its way, you'll receive a tracking number to monitor its journey from our warehouse to your doorstep. With real-time updates, you'll always know where your package is, giving you peace of mind and the power to plan accordingly.</p>",
            "text_alignment": "text-left"
          }
        },
        "shipping-2": {
          "type": "icon",
          "settings": {
            "icon_name": "icon-chat",
            "icon_size": 20,
            "icon_color": "#32393e",
            "title": "Get in touch",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-small",
            "icon_alignment": "left",
            "text": "<p>We're here to assist you every step of the way. If you have any questions, concerns, or just want to say hello, don't hesitate to get in touch with our friendly customer support team. Reach out through our contact page, and we'll be more than happy to help with any inquiries or assistance you may need. Your satisfaction is our priority.</p>",
            "text_alignment": "text-left"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
